SubjectOrder Amending Schedule 1 to the First Nations Goods and Services Tax Act (Leq'à:mel First Nation)
PrecisOrder Amending Schedule 1 to the FIRST NATIONS GOODS AND SERVICES TAX ACT (LEQ'À:MEL FIRST NATION) in order to enable the Leq'à:mel First Nation, with the agreement of the Government of Canda, to implement a FNGST within its reserves that are not shared with any other bands.
